{"word":"κληρονόμος","slug":"κληρονόμος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰληρονόμος, ου, ὁ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κλῆρος\">κλῆρος</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:νόμος\">νόμος</a></el> (in sense of that which is apportioned, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el>νέμω, νέμομαι</el> ‘hold as portion’)]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘inheritor in legal sense’, <b>heir <a href='B:470 21:38'>Mt 21:38</a>; <a href='B:480 12:7'>Mk 12:7</a>; <a href='B:490 20:14'>Lk 20:14</a>; <a href='B:550 4:1'>Gal 4:1</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> participant in a share’, <b>heir,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on divinely promised benefit(s) <b><a href='B:520 4:13'>Ro 4:13f</a>; <a href='B:520 8:17'>8:17</a>; <a href='B:550 3:29'>Gal 3:29</a>; <a href='B:550 4:7'>4:7</a>; <a href='B:630 3:7'>Tit 3:7</a>; <a href='B:650 1:2'>Hb 1:2</a>; <a href='B:650 6:17'>6:17</a>; <a href='B:650 11:7'>11:7</a>; <a href='B:660 2:5'>Js 2:5</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κληρονομία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κλῆρος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}